{"tid":2456170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"200萬人簽名，30萬人接種，似咩樣？！無打針，根本無資格做藍絲！","createTime":"2021-03-21T16:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T04:01:19.000Z","uid":257533,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c4d71f5667a3ffc294b9f50baacee0dbc7601bf7","tid":2456170,"uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:46:37.000Z","msg":"唔係話要鬥藍，<br />\n但政府已經開放疫苗計劃畀30歲以上人士，<br />\n為咗香港好，為咗香港嘅經濟好，<br />\n為咗國家好，<br />\n為人又好，為己又好，<br />\n為200萬都好，<br />\n身為藍絲，點解唔接種！！<br />\n<br />\n我唔想我地藍絲，繼續一世畀人睇唔起！<br />\n我唔想譚耀宗畀人睇唔起！<br />\n我唔想畀人知道我地簽個名都要做假！<br />\n我唔想輸呀！！！而家輸晒啦！！"},{"pid":"06ff62f12742b62d5cdcdffd02f7180ffce84a51","tid":2456170,"uid":257533,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:55:24.000Z","msg":"你睇譚sir個樣幾攰，你就知佢為咗香港付出咗幾多心血！<br />\n<br />\n黃屍唔好諗住屈佢打完科興搞到咁！<br />\n佢係打國藥的！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRSLSko.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRSLSko.png&h=c0128067&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f330ba35d375da26088e0be4baf88df431687f4","tid":2456170,"uid":393145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:57:16.000Z","msg":"偽藍港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為搞藍色簽名圈就係愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要打針時就返工驚死不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n200萬人簽名 去晒邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得少少人打針<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推啲老人家去送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n輸喇 藍營輸晒喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406d9a3901654c9255958dec1d754c918971a7cd","tid":2456170,"uid":169529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:12:58.000Z","msg":"藍友針又唔打藍店又唔食富臨都執埋<br />\n實一世比黃屍睇死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfba